@startuml

title The Firm — Workflow Phases, Gates, and Artifact Flow
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #4B5563
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #374151
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam PackageBorderColor #374151
skinparam PackageBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFF7D6
skinparam NoteBorderColor #D6B656
skinparam roundcorner 12

legend right
  Source basis:
  * THE_FIRM_WORKFLOW_ARCHITECTURE.md
  * THE_FIRM_OPERATING_MODEL.md
endlegend

rectangle "Phase 0\nIntake\nOwner: Product" as p0
rectangle "Phase 1\nProduct Framing\nArtifacts:\nvision.md\nproduct-brief.md\nacceptance.md" as p1
rectangle "Gate 1\nProduct Readiness" as g1
rectangle "Phase 2\nTechnical Discovery\nArtifacts:\ntechnical-discovery.md\ncallsite impact\nstate flow notes" as p2
rectangle "Gate 2\nDiscovery Completeness" as g2
rectangle "Phase 3\nDesign Lock\nArtifacts:\ntechnical-design.md\ncontracts\nverification mapping\nwave plan" as p3
rectangle "Gate 3\nDesign Lock" as g3
rectangle "Phase 4\nDelivery Planning\nArtifacts:\ndelivery-plan.md\nexecution waves\nengineering handoff" as p4
rectangle "Gate 4\nDelivery Readiness" as g4
rectangle "Phase 5\nImplementation Waves\nArtifacts:\ncode\ntests\nimplementation notes" as p5
rectangle "Gate 5\nQA Entry" as g5
rectangle "Phase 6\nQA & Verification\nArtifacts:\nqa-verdict.md\npropagation verdicts\nE2E notes\nresidual risk notes" as p6
rectangle "Gate 6\nVerification Complete" as g6
rectangle "Phase 7\nRelease Readiness / Closure\nArtifacts:\nrelease-readiness.md\nclosure records" as p7
rectangle "Gate 7\nFinal Closure" as g7
rectangle "Phase 8\nRetrospective\nArtifacts:\nretro.md" as p8

p0 --> p1
p1 --> g1
g1 --> p2 : if acceptance intent exists
p2 --> g2
g2 --> p3 : if surfaces and constraints are known
p3 --> g3
g3 --> p4 : if contracts + verification are locked
p4 --> g4
g4 --> p5 : if waves, owners, dependencies are explicit
p5 --> g5
g5 --> p6 : if QA intake is possible
p6 --> g6
g6 --> p7 : if evidence is sufficient
p7 --> g7
g7 --> p8 : if closure is process-valid

note bottom of p3
  Design package should include C4 views,
  sequence/state-flow diagrams, ADR-style decisions,
  integration boundaries, and verification mapping.
end note

note bottom of p6
  Propagation and E2E checks are required when
  the change affects shared state or critical flows.
end note

note bottom of g7
  Closure requires explicit release confidence,
  resolved or accepted blockers, and artifact linkage.
end note
@enduml
